                    <p>The School systems are under great pressure to cope with the emerging challenges and make their School Campus tech savvy and their pedagogy learner friendly.</p>
                    <p>The changing School structures are looking for concept Schools, ecofriendly Schools and Wired Schools. The question therefore arises as to what makes a School a good School? Is it it’s technology, environment? Or is it the magnificent infrastructure? Or Is it it’s culture of pedagogy? Is it it’s result in Board Exams? Or is it a kind of corporate culture that takes care of customer needs?</p>
                    <p>The soul of a good School lies in its humanistic approach, the attitude to the growth and development process of the learners and the passion to generate a community of nation builders.</p>
